    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "what do you mean by letting go of the weight? it feels like the weight is just... me. everything i touch breaks. my family, my career, my reputation. it's not just a bad patch, it's a permanent stain. how do you even \"let go\" of the fact that you've failed everyone?",
