      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not that simple though. the people i care about... they don't see a \"new person,\" they just see the person who lost everything. the shame isn't something i can just \"accept\" and move past. it's all i am now. i feel like there's no version of my future where this doesn't follow me forever. i just want the noise to stop. i want the feeling of being a failure to just... end.",
